<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>SVS — About</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <style>
    :root{
      --amber:#FACC15; --amber-dark:#EAB308; --blue:#1D4ED8; --red:#DC2626; --bg:#e9f0ff; --bg-2:#fff7ef; --surface:#ffffff;
      --text:#0F172A; --muted:#475569; --muted2:#64748B; --border:#c8d7f3; --border-mid:#97BDE9;
      --shadow-md:0 12px 32px rgba(15,23,42,.12);
    }
    *{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0;}
    body{font-family:'Outfit',sans-serif;background:radial-gradient(800px 480px at 10% 12%,rgba(29,78,216,.08),transparent 60%),radial-gradient(760px 520px at 120% -10%,rgba(220,38,38,.08),transparent 62%),linear-gradient(180deg,#f4f7ff 0%,#fff9ef 82%,#ffffff 100%);color:var(--text);-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;line-height:1.65;}
    a{color:var(--blue);text-decoration:none;}
    a:visited{color:var(--blue);}
    a:hover{color:#0f3fb5;}
    header{position:sticky;top:0;z-index:10;display:grid;grid-template-columns:auto 1fr auto;align-items:center;gap:1rem;padding:1rem 1.5rem;background:rgba(243,247,255,.9);backdrop-filter:blur(18px);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(191,214,245,.9);box-shadow:0 6px 18px rgba(0,0,0,.08);color:var(--text);}
    .brand{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.6rem;color:var(--text);}
    .brand img{width:72px;height:60px;object-fit:contain;}
    .brand-text{line-height:1;}
    .brand-name{font-weight:900;font-size:1.25rem;letter-spacing:-.2px;color:var(--text);}
    .brand-sub{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:.7rem;letter-spacing:1px;color:#475569;}
    .header-right{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr auto;align-items:center;gap:.7rem;width:100%;justify-items:center;}
    .nav-links{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.65rem;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center;}
        .nav-btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:.5rem 1.1rem;border:1.6px solid rgba(151,189,233,.9);border-radius:15px;color:var(--text);font-weight:820;font-size:.9rem;transition:.16s;background:linear-gradient(180deg,#fff,#f3f7ff);box-shadow:0 9px 18px rgba(15,23,42,.08);}
        .nav-btn:hover{border-color:var(--blue);color:var(--blue);box-shadow:0 12px 24px rgba(29,78,216,.15);}
        .nav-btn.active{border-color:var(--blue);background:linear-gradient(180deg,#f0f5ff,#dfe9ff);color:var(--blue);box-shadow:0 12px 26px rgba(29,78,216,.22);}
        .main-datetime{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;min-height:56px;padding:.65rem 1rem;background:linear-gradient(180deg,#ffffff,#eef3ff) padding-box,linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(239,68,68,.9),rgba(59,130,246,.9)) border-box;border:1.6px solid transparent;border-radius:18px;color:#0F172A;white-space:nowrap;box-shadow:0 14px 26px rgba(0,0,0,.08), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.65);backdrop-filter:blur(10px);}
        .main-datetime svg{width:22px;height:18px;stroke:var(--blue);fill:none;stroke-width:2;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;flex-shrink:0;}
    .time-block{display:flex;flex-direction:column;line-height:1.05;min-width:0;}
        .clock-text{font-family:'Orbitron','JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:1.08rem;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:1.1px;color:#0b1a3a;}
        .date-text{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:.7rem;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:.8px;color:#4b5563;margin-top:3px;}
    .hero{max-width:1180px;margin:2.6rem auto 1.8rem;padding:1.25rem 1.5rem;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.05fr .95fr;gap:1.8rem;align-items:center;border:1.4px solid #d8e5ff;border-radius:26px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(255,255,255,.82),rgba(238,246,255,.9));box-shadow:0 20px 38px rgba(15,23,42,.1);}
    .hero h1{font-size:3.15rem;line-height:1.08;letter-spacing:-1.15px;margin-bottom:1rem;color:#0c1a36;}
    .hero h1 em{font-style:normal;color:var(--red);}
    .hero p{color:#1f2937;font-size:1.08rem;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:1.5rem;}
    .cta-row{display:flex;gap:.75rem;flex-wrap:wrap;}
    .btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:.85rem 1.4rem;border-radius:12px;border:1.5px solid var(--border-mid);font-weight:800;cursor:pointer;transition:.18s;}
    .btn.primary{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ef4444,#dc2626);color:#fff;border-color:transparent;box-shadow:var(--shadow-md);}
    .btn.secondary{background:#fff;color:var(--blue);}
    .btn:hover{transform:translateY(-1px);}
    .pill{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;border-radius:999px;background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--border-mid);padding:.5rem .9rem;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:.8rem;font-weight:700;color:#0f3fb5;box-shadow:0 8px 22px rgba(15,23,42,.08);}
    .cards{max-width:1180px;margin:0 auto 2.8rem;padding:0 1.25rem;display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(260px,1fr));gap:1.1rem;counter-reset:step;}
    .card{background:linear-gradient(180deg,#f8fbff,#eef4ff);border:1.6px solid #bed6fa;border-radius:18px;padding:1.4rem 1.5rem;box-shadow:0 16px 36px rgba(15,23,42,.12);}
    .card.step{position:relative;padding-left:5rem;}
    .hotline-section{max-width:1180px;margin:0 auto 2.8rem;padding:1.25rem;}
    .hotline-section h3{font-size:1.65rem;color:#0c1a36;margin-bottom:.9rem;}
    .hotline-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:1rem;}
    .hotline-card{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.75rem;border:1.5px solid #c8d7f3;border-radius:14px;background:linear-gradient(180deg,#f8fbff,#fff);padding:.9rem;box-shadow:0 10px 22px rgba(15,23,42,.12);}
    .hotline-card img{width:42px;height:42px;object-fit:contain;border-radius:8px;}
    .hotline-card .hotline-link{flex:1;display:grid;gap:.25rem;}
    .hotline-card .hotline-link a{font-weight:800;color:#1d4ed8;}
    .hotline-card .hotline-link p{margin:0;color:#0f172a;font-size:.94rem;}
    .hotline-phonenumber{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:.95rem;font-weight:700;color:#dc2626;}    .card.step::before{
      content: attr(data-step);
      position:absolute;left:1rem;top:1.1rem;
      width:38px;height:38px;border-radius:12px;
      background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1D4ED8,#2563EB);
      color:#fff;font-weight:900;font-size:.95rem;display:grid;place-items:center;
      box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(29,78,216,.25);
    }
    .card h3{font-size:1.15rem;margin-bottom:.45rem;color:#0f3fb5;}
    .card p{color:#14213d;line-height:1.6;font-size:1rem;}
    .summary-card{
      background:linear-gradient(180deg,#f4f7ff,#eef3ff);
      border:1.6px solid #cbdcfe;
      border-radius:20px;
      padding:1.5rem 1.6rem;
      box-shadow:0 18px 34px rgba(15,23,42,.12);
    }
    .summary-card h3{margin:0 0 .6rem;font-size:1.25rem;color:#0c1a36;}
    .summary-card ul{margin:.2rem 0 0 1.1rem;color:#1f2937;line-height:1.6;font-size:1.02rem;}
    .summary-card li{margin-bottom:.35rem;}
    .summary-eyebrow{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:.78rem;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:1.2px;color:#1D4ED8;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:.35rem;}
    .site-footer{
      margin-top:3rem;
      background:linear-gradient(180deg,#eaf2ff 0%,#fff7ef 90%);
      border-top:1px solid var(--border);
      padding:2.2rem 1.5rem 2.6rem;
      color:var(--text);
      box-shadow:0 -6px 24px rgba(15,23,42,.06);
    }
    .footer-grid{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:2rem;align-items:flex-start;}
    .footer-brand{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1rem;}
    .footer-brand img{width:64px;height:64px;object-fit:contain;}
    .footer-brand h4{margin:0;font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:-.2px;}
    .footer-tag{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:.75rem;font-weight:700;color:#1D4ED8;letter-spacing:1.4px;text-transform:uppercase;}
    .footer-copy{margin-top:.6rem;color:#1f2937;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.6;}
    .footer-contact h5{letter-spacing:1px;font-size:.75rem;font-weight:800;color:#1D4ED8;margin:0 0 .5rem;}
    .footer-contact p{margin:.15rem 0;color:#0f172a;font-weight:700;}
    .footer-line{height:1px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(59,130,246,.3),transparent);margin:1.2rem 0;}
    .footer-meta{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:1rem;color:#475569;font-size:.9rem;}
    @media(max-width:760px){.footer-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;} .footer-meta{flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-start;}}
    @media(max-width:860px){.hero{grid-template-columns:1fr;} .hero h1{font-size:2.35rem;}}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <a class="brand" href="/about">
      <img src="/images/logo.png" alt="SVS logo">
      <div class="brand-text">
        <div class="brand-name">SVS</div>
        <div class="brand-sub">Smart Verification System</div>
      </div>
    </a>
    <div class="header-right" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr auto;align-items:center;gap:.7rem;width:100%;">
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a class="nav-btn" href="/sos">SOS</a>
        <a class="nav-btn" href="/report">Report</a>
        <a class="nav-btn active" href="/about">About Us</a>
        <a class="nav-btn" href="/faq">FAQ</a>
      </div>
      <div class="main-datetime" id="aboutTime">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M6.75 3v2.25m10.5-2.25v2.25M3.75 9.75h16.5M4.5 5.25h15A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 21 6.75v12A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 19.5 20.25h-15A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 3 18.75v-12A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 4.5 5.25Z"/></svg>
        <div class="time-block"><span class="clock-text">--:--:--</span><span class="date-text">Loading...</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="hero">
    <div>
      <div class="pill">The problem → The solution</div>
      <h1>From clogged hotlines to clear, verified emergency reports.</h1>
      <p>Emergency lines used to drown in prank calls, vague landmarks, and dropped signals. SVS was built with responders to verify callers, pin locations automatically, and keep genuine emergencies moving fast.</p>
      <div class="cta-row">
        <a class="btn primary" href="/report">File an Emergency Report</a>
        <a class="btn secondary" href="/sos">Quick SOS options</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="summary-card">
      <div class="summary-eyebrow">Site overview</div>
      <h3>Everything in one place.</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Learn the history of the emergency-reporting bottleneck.</li>
        <li>See the solution: GPS-first SOS, verification, and offline queueing.</li>
        <li>Trigger an SOS or file a verified report when seconds matter.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cards">
    <div class="card step" data-step="01">
      <h3>Before SVS</h3>
      <p>Hotlines were flooded with prank calls, vague landmarks, and no GPS, slowing real dispatch work.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card step" data-step="02">
      <h3>What had to change</h3>
      <p>We needed caller verification, automatic location capture, and a way to keep signals alive when networks drop.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card step" data-step="03">
      <h3>Our Solution</h3>
      <p>GPS-first SOS, identity checks, and offline queueing send clean, verified reports to dispatchers in seconds.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card step" data-step="04">
      <h3>Results for Teams</h3>
      <p>Faster triage, fewer false alarms, clearer routes, and better focus on life-saving responses.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

